WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:47.090 --> 00:00:50.050
[insects chirping]

3
00:00:51.790 --> 00:00:54.706
[unsettling music playing]

4
00:01:00.016 --> 00:01:02.932
[birds calling]

5
00:01:03.976 --> 00:01:06.936
[♪]

6
00:01:07.893 --> 00:01:09.765
[Boy] <i>[VO] This was never
a great city.</i>

7
00:01:10.896 --> 00:01:13.485
<i>Hilda Van Der Koy
took it from us.</i>

8
00:01:13.486 --> 00:01:16.076
<i>This is how she keeps control.</i>

9
00:01:17.425 --> 00:01:20.645
<i>They call it The Culling.</i>

10
00:01:20.646 --> 00:01:22.168
[crowd protesting]

11
00:01:22.169 --> 00:01:24.779
[Boy] <i>[VO] It happens
the same day every year;</i>

12
00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:29.284
<i>a twisted demonstration
to strike fear in our people.</i>

13
00:01:29.285 --> 00:01:33.789
<i>Every year. she makes a list
of all her enemies.</i>

14
00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:36.226
<i>If your name's on it.</i>

15
00:01:38.881 --> 00:01:40.622
<i>she'll find you.</i>

16
00:01:41.971 --> 00:01:44.539
[birds calling]

17
00:01:48.020 --> 00:01:50.805
[cries]

18
00:01:50.806 --> 00:01:53.025
[rapid gunshots]

19
00:01:54.375 --> 00:01:57.987
[thunder clapping.
rain pattering]

20
00:01:58.901 --> 00:02:01.773
[dramatic music playing]

21
00:02:13.394 --> 00:02:16.136
[animal calling]

22
00:02:29.366 --> 00:02:31.673
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Hilda took everything from me.</i>

23
00:02:33.805 --> 00:02:36.156
<i>and when I become
the ultimate warrior...</i>

24
00:02:37.809 --> 00:02:40.029
<i>I'm gonna return the favor.</i>

25
00:02:41.378 --> 00:02:44.773
<i>But for now.
I'm buried alive...</i>

26
00:02:47.297 --> 00:02:48.950
<i>eating stinkbugs.</i>

27
00:02:48.951 --> 00:02:50.605
[sucks stinkbug]

28
00:02:51.519 --> 00:02:54.826
[intense music playing]

29
00:03:03.487 --> 00:03:06.621
[ethereal music playing]

30
00:03:12.453 --> 00:03:15.325
[breathing hard]

31
00:03:21.810 --> 00:03:23.637
<i>I failed.</i>

32
00:03:23.638 --> 00:03:26.030
<i>Back to the hole.</i>

33
00:03:26.031 --> 00:03:27.207
<i>Can't be too angry.</i>

34
00:03:27.208 --> 00:03:28.337
[straining]

35
00:03:28.338 --> 00:03:30.166
<i>I signed up for this.</i>

36
00:03:31.994 --> 00:03:34.452
<i>I guess I just
expected training</i>

37
00:03:34.453 --> 00:03:36.912
<i>to involve less... dirt.</i>

38
00:03:48.619 --> 00:03:51.143
[birds chirping]

39
00:03:58.325 --> 00:04:00.304
[rapid punching]

40
00:04:00.305 --> 00:04:02.796
[young Boy grunts]

41
00:04:02.797 --> 00:04:05.288
[action music playing]

42
00:04:05.289 --> 00:04:06.767
[Shaman groans]

43
00:04:06.768 --> 00:04:09.074
[Boy] <i>[VO] The Shaman says
to be a great warrior.</i>

44
00:04:09.075 --> 00:04:11.381
<i>I have to stop acting
like a little boy.</i>

45
00:04:11.382 --> 00:04:12.729
<i>Little boys get distracted.</i>

46
00:04:12.730 --> 00:04:15.211
<i>Little boys hate doing chores.</i>

47
00:04:15.212 --> 00:04:16.864
<i>Not me.</i>

48
00:04:16.865 --> 00:04:21.565
<i>I'm the tidiest assassin.
super clean and super deadly.</i>

49
00:04:21.566 --> 00:04:23.524
- [gun fired]
- [young Boy] Ah! [groans]

50
00:04:23.525 --> 00:04:25.176
[Shaman laughing]

51
00:04:25.177 --> 00:04:26.657
[Boy] <i>[VO] In my downtime.
I like to hang out</i>

52
00:04:26.658 --> 00:04:28.528
<i>with my best friends.</i>

53
00:04:28.529 --> 00:04:32.141
<i>Gabe and Alfonzo. champions
of Beetle Fight Club.</i>

54
00:04:33.316 --> 00:04:35.231
<i>Until it got canceled.</i>

55
00:04:35.232 --> 00:04:36.797
[drum beating]

56
00:04:36.798 --> 00:04:39.583
<i>Shaman says warriors
don't need friends.</i>

57
00:04:39.584 --> 00:04:40.888
<i>- Or food.</i>
- [Shaman burps]

58
00:04:40.889 --> 00:04:42.194
[Boy] <i>[VO] Apparently.</i>

59
00:04:42.195 --> 00:04:44.414
[liquid boiling]

60
00:04:49.376 --> 00:04:52.029
<i>Just keep reading
the dictionary.</i>

61
00:04:52.030 --> 00:04:56.513
<i>Gotta stop thinking
about food... And Mina.</i>

62
00:04:57.471 --> 00:04:59.668
<i>Frosty Puffs every morning.</i>

63
00:04:59.669 --> 00:05:01.865
<i>It was the best.</i>

64
00:05:01.866 --> 00:05:03.737
["Frosty Puffs" theme
playing on TV]

65
00:05:03.738 --> 00:05:05.609
<i>I know Mom was a little...</i>

66
00:05:07.002 --> 00:05:08.308
<i>intense.</i>

67
00:05:10.745 --> 00:05:13.835
<i>I don't remember much
from before the incident.</i>

68
00:05:13.836 --> 00:05:16.663
<i>But I do remember Mina.</i>

69
00:05:16.664 --> 00:05:18.491
Which is why
I formed a plan for us

70
00:05:18.492 --> 00:05:20.320
to escape this
totalitarian hellhole.

71
00:05:20.321 --> 00:05:22.843
[plate shatters]

72
00:05:22.844 --> 00:05:25.412
It's all here in this diagram.

73
00:05:25.413 --> 00:05:26.674
You with me?

74
00:05:27.501 --> 00:05:28.719
[Boy] <i>[VO] Always.</i>

75
00:05:31.243 --> 00:05:34.224
<i>I can't remember what
I sounded like back then.</i>

76
00:05:34.225 --> 00:05:36.520
[Game Boy] <i>[VO]
Super Dragon Punch Force 2.</i>

77
00:05:36.521 --> 00:05:38.815
<i>Player Two
has entered the game.</i>

78
00:05:38.816 --> 00:05:40.296
[Boy] <i>[VO] That's why
I gave myself</i>

79
00:05:40.297 --> 00:05:42.863
<i>this super cool voice.</i>

80
00:05:42.864 --> 00:05:44.800
<i>I took it from
our favorite video game.</i>

81
00:05:44.801 --> 00:05:46.736
[Game Boy] <i>[VO]
Player Two wins.</i>

82
00:05:46.737 --> 00:05:48.304
[Boy] <i>[VO]
We were happy then.</i>

83
00:05:51.612 --> 00:05:53.744
<i>[wistful] Some things
are hard to forget.</i>

84
00:05:56.486 --> 00:05:57.747
<i>Liminal.</i>

85
00:05:57.748 --> 00:06:00.403
<i>To exist between two states.</i>

86
00:06:01.926 --> 00:06:05.365
<i>Awake and asleep
at the same time.</i>

87
00:06:05.366 --> 00:06:07.844
[laughing]

88
00:06:07.845 --> 00:06:10.042
[Boy] <i>[VO]
That's how I feel these days.</i>

89
00:06:10.043 --> 00:06:12.241
<i>especially when we go to the city.</i>

90
00:06:14.374 --> 00:06:15.374
[wet squelch]

91
00:06:15.375 --> 00:06:16.376
[knife clanks]

92
00:06:18.856 --> 00:06:22.164
<i>Never sure how much of what
I'm seeing is real anymore.</i>

93
00:06:22.165 --> 00:06:24.208
[laughing]

94
00:06:24.209 --> 00:06:26.429
[woman speaking
in foreign language]

95
00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:27.778
[hyena laughing]

96
00:06:28.823 --> 00:06:30.259
[woman] Can I get apples?

97
00:06:32.653 --> 00:06:33.870
Where is this?

98
00:06:33.871 --> 00:06:35.525
What is this. huh?
What do you have one?

99
00:06:35.526 --> 00:06:37.091
Let's go.

100
00:06:37.092 --> 00:06:39.311
This market's no place
for little boys.

101
00:06:39.312 --> 00:06:40.704
Run to your mommy.

102
00:06:40.705 --> 00:06:43.533
[low chatter]

103
00:06:48.538 --> 00:06:50.104
[Boy] <i>[VO] Can't hear.</i>

104
00:06:50.105 --> 00:06:51.625
<i>but I'm getting better
at reading lips.</i>

105
00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:55.371
<i>It beats talking
to these assholes.</i>

106
00:06:58.243 --> 00:07:00.941
[chicken clucking]

107
00:07:00.942 --> 00:07:03.639
<i>Mina...</i>

108
00:07:03.640 --> 00:07:04.815
- [Mina giggling]
- [Boy] <i>[VO] I still see her</i>

109
00:07:04.816 --> 00:07:06.795
<i>everywhere I go.</i>

110
00:07:06.796 --> 00:07:08.775
[Mina laughs]

111
00:07:08.776 --> 00:07:10.430
[Boy] <i>[VO]
She made everything fun.</i>

112
00:07:13.998 --> 00:07:16.131
[Mina] She's the reason
everything's the worst.

113
00:07:17.219 --> 00:07:19.656
They're all afraid.
but not me.

114
00:07:19.657 --> 00:07:20.962
Watch.

115
00:07:23.660 --> 00:07:25.836
I just gave her
the middle finger five times

116
00:07:25.837 --> 00:07:28.273
because it's all
five fingers at once.

117
00:07:28.274 --> 00:07:29.360
Try it.

118
00:07:29.361 --> 00:07:31.014
[Boy] <i>[VO] That was my sister.</i>

119
00:07:31.015 --> 00:07:34.976
<i>She wasn't scared of anything.
Not even Hilda Van Der Koy.</i>

120
00:07:37.108 --> 00:07:39.370
<i>We were naive.</i>

121
00:07:39.371 --> 00:07:42.069
- [insects chirping]
- [liquid boiling]

122
00:07:42.070 --> 00:07:44.680
[Boy] <i>[VO] Shaman says
our memories make us weak.</i>

123
00:07:44.681 --> 00:07:47.292
[Shaman] <i>[VO]
You are no longer a child.</i>

124
00:07:48.511 --> 00:07:51.948
<i>All that you once were
is dead.</i>

125
00:07:51.949 --> 00:07:54.082
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Warriors can't be weak.</i>

126
00:07:54.083 --> 00:07:56.300
Aaahhh!

127
00:07:56.301 --> 00:08:01.916
[Boy] <i>[VO] I am an instrument
shaped for a single purpose:</i>

128
00:08:01.917 --> 00:08:04.679
<i>to kill Hilda Van Der Koy.</i>

129
00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:07.442
<i>Show me the way.</i>

130
00:08:07.443 --> 00:08:09.967
["I Get Mine" performed
by El Michels Affair playing]

131
00:08:11.839 --> 00:08:13.448
<i>♪ La la</i>

132
00:08:13.449 --> 00:08:15.494
[both grunting]

133
00:08:15.495 --> 00:08:19.759
<i>♪ La la la la</i>

134
00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:24.895
<i>♪ La la la</i>
- [Boy straining]

135
00:08:24.896 --> 00:08:26.287
<i>♪ La la la la</i>

136
00:08:26.288 --> 00:08:27.855
[Boy] <i>[VO] I will kill
Hilda Van Der Koy.</i>

137
00:08:27.856 --> 00:08:29.682
[grunts]

138
00:08:29.683 --> 00:08:32.293
[stabs knife]
<i>I will make you proud.</i>

139
00:08:32.294 --> 00:08:37.428
[Shaman] <i>[VO] I'm already
proud. and I love you.</i>

140
00:08:37.429 --> 00:08:38.779
[Boy] <i>[VO] He's not really
saying this. is he?</i>

141
00:08:38.780 --> 00:08:40.040
[laughing]

142
00:08:40.041 --> 00:08:41.998
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Yup. this is in my head.</i>

143
00:08:41.999 --> 00:08:44.306
- [Shaman laughing]
- [Boy] <i>[VO] Eye bubbles.</i>

144
00:08:44.307 --> 00:08:46.134
[straining]

145
00:08:48.963 --> 00:08:52.140
[punches thrown]

146
00:08:54.751 --> 00:08:55.751
[knife clanks]

147
00:08:57.232 --> 00:08:59.669
- [kick thrown]
- [rapid gunfire]

148
00:08:59.670 --> 00:09:02.977
[Cereal Sailor laughing]

149
00:09:03.673 --> 00:09:06.546
[young Boy grunting]

150
00:09:09.679 --> 00:09:10.723
Ah!

151
00:09:10.724 --> 00:09:12.464
[huge head rolling]

152
00:09:13.509 --> 00:09:16.468
[panting]

153
00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:20.081
[Shaman's evil laugh]

154
00:09:21.996 --> 00:09:23.387
[Boy] <i>[VO] Ameliorate.</i>

155
00:09:23.388 --> 00:09:26.391
<i>To improve in the face of
great struggle.</i>

156
00:09:29.003 --> 00:09:32.136
[exciting music playing]

157
00:09:34.182 --> 00:09:35.879
[stick whipping through the air]

158
00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:41.493
<i>I am ready.</i>

159
00:09:44.496 --> 00:09:47.325
[overlapping grunting]

160
00:09:48.239 --> 00:09:51.394
[exciting music playing]

161
00:09:51.395 --> 00:09:54.550
[overlapping grunting]

162
00:10:12.394 --> 00:10:15.353
[Boy grunting]

163
00:10:15.354 --> 00:10:18.313
[laughing]

164
00:10:21.751 --> 00:10:22.796
[teeth falling out]

165
00:10:28.889 --> 00:10:31.891
[teeth chattering]

166
00:10:31.892 --> 00:10:34.982
[intense. exciting music
playing]

167
00:10:40.465 --> 00:10:43.425
[overlapping grunting]

168
00:10:48.169 --> 00:10:51.346
[intense. exciting music
playing]

169
00:10:55.524 --> 00:10:57.591
[pulleys squeak]

170
00:10:57.592 --> 00:10:59.659
[rapid gunfire]

171
00:11:07.928 --> 00:11:09.799
- [kick thrown]
- [Boy grunts]

172
00:11:12.497 --> 00:11:15.413
- [kick and punch thrown]
- [overlapping grunting]

173
00:11:27.077 --> 00:11:29.950
[Boy grunting]

174
00:11:37.522 --> 00:11:40.395
You are not ready. Boy.

175
00:11:46.009 --> 00:11:49.230
[insects chirping]

176
00:11:50.231 --> 00:11:51.448
[struck bowl rings]

177
00:11:51.449 --> 00:11:53.974
[Boy] <i>[VO] Focus.
Focus on the...</i>

178
00:11:53.975 --> 00:11:54.974
[Mina crunching]

179
00:11:54.975 --> 00:11:56.976
<i>What was that?</i>

180
00:11:56.977 --> 00:11:58.064
[struck bowl rings]

181
00:11:58.065 --> 00:12:00.502
<i>Ignore it.
Just think of...</i>

182
00:12:00.503 --> 00:12:01.676
[Mina crunching]

183
00:12:01.677 --> 00:12:02.939
<i>Okay. this is all
in your head.</i>

184
00:12:03.810 --> 00:12:06.768
[Mina crunching]

185
00:12:06.769 --> 00:12:08.902
<i>Doesn't matter. Focus.</i>

186
00:12:08.903 --> 00:12:12.556
[loud crunching]

187
00:12:12.557 --> 00:12:15.430
<i>Okay. why did your head
give her potato chips?</i>

188
00:12:18.041 --> 00:12:20.740
<i>Just don't make eye contact.</i>

189
00:12:24.178 --> 00:12:26.746
<i>If you don't look at her.
then she isn't there.</i>

190
00:12:29.705 --> 00:12:30.705
<i>Damn it.</i>

191
00:12:30.706 --> 00:12:33.622
[pleasing music plays]

192
00:12:41.325 --> 00:12:44.153
<i>Repeat the mantra.
I am a weapon.</i>

193
00:12:44.154 --> 00:12:47.178
<i>Shaped for a single purpose.</i>

194
00:12:47.179 --> 00:12:50.204
<i>No distractions. Focus.</i>

195
00:12:50.857 --> 00:12:54.121
[overlapping chatter]

196
00:13:00.214 --> 00:13:02.042
- [giggles]
- [Boy] <i>[VO] What?</i>

197
00:13:02.043 --> 00:13:04.392
[romantic music playing]

198
00:13:04.393 --> 00:13:05.784
<i>Oh.</i>

199
00:13:05.785 --> 00:13:08.396
[song playing]

200
00:13:25.326 --> 00:13:26.587
[Boy] <i>[VO] Resplendent.</i>

201
00:13:26.588 --> 00:13:29.330
<i>To have a pleasant
glowing quality.</i>

202
00:13:30.200 --> 00:13:32.898
[car approaching]

203
00:13:32.899 --> 00:13:34.814
[Anna] The Van Der Koys.

204
00:13:34.815 --> 00:13:36.163
They're coming.

205
00:13:38.992 --> 00:13:40.862
[car engine revs]

206
00:13:40.863 --> 00:13:42.473
[VDK soldier] Go. go. go!

207
00:13:43.605 --> 00:13:44.910
Let's go. This way.

208
00:13:44.911 --> 00:13:46.520
I love The Culling. don't you?

209
00:13:46.521 --> 00:13:48.196
[voice over speaker]
<i>...instructions.</i>

210
00:13:48.197 --> 00:13:49.872
<i>All citizens
are required to...</i>

211
00:13:49.873 --> 00:13:51.831
What is wrong with you?

212
00:13:53.180 --> 00:13:55.116
[voice over speaker]
<i>...parties.</i>

213
00:13:55.117 --> 00:13:57.052
<i>Order must be maintained.</i>

214
00:13:57.053 --> 00:14:00.752
<i>Any attempt to disrupt
will be met with consequences.</i>

215
00:14:00.753 --> 00:14:02.797
<i>All citizens
must follow regulations</i>

216
00:14:02.798 --> 00:14:05.582
<i>set forth
by the Van Der Koy family.</i>

217
00:14:05.583 --> 00:14:09.022
<i>Any attempts to resist
or undermine the authority...</i>

218
00:14:09.023 --> 00:14:11.720
- Don't resist. Let's go.
- [citizen groaning]

219
00:14:14.201 --> 00:14:15.571
[chaotic shouting]

220
00:14:15.572 --> 00:14:16.943
[VDK soldier] Come on!

221
00:14:16.944 --> 00:14:18.378
Get back!

222
00:14:18.379 --> 00:14:19.815
[voice over speaker]
<i>All citizens are required</i>

223
00:14:19.816 --> 00:14:21.250
<i>by Van Der Koy law</i>

224
00:14:21.251 --> 00:14:23.949
<i>to immediately report
to the square.</i>

225
00:14:23.950 --> 00:14:26.125
<i>Resistance will be punished.</i>

226
00:14:26.126 --> 00:14:28.302
<i>Have a lovely day.</i>

227
00:14:31.914 --> 00:14:33.960
- [rapid gunfire]
- [VDK soldier] Turn around.

228
00:14:33.961 --> 00:14:35.962
- [woman grunts]
- [VDK soldier] Move!

229
00:14:35.963 --> 00:14:38.747
[man] Stay there. hey!

230
00:14:38.748 --> 00:14:40.401
[woman grunting]

231
00:14:42.925 --> 00:14:45.841
[insidious music plays]

232
00:14:50.933 --> 00:14:52.935
[Anna] Mister Van Der Koy.

233
00:14:52.936 --> 00:14:54.066
Hey.

234
00:14:54.067 --> 00:14:55.241
Can you maybe sign this
for me. please?

235
00:14:55.242 --> 00:14:56.417
- Oh. sure. Sure. sweetie.
- Thanks.

236
00:14:56.418 --> 00:14:57.940
- What's your name?
- Anna.

237
00:14:57.941 --> 00:14:59.201
Anna.

238
00:14:59.202 --> 00:15:00.681
[Anna] Thanks for all you do
for the city.

239
00:15:00.682 --> 00:15:01.944
- [Glen] Oh. you're welcome.
- [Anna] Long live Hilda.

240
00:15:01.945 --> 00:15:04.077
[Glen] Yes. Ha-ha!

241
00:15:04.078 --> 00:15:04.990
Whoo!

242
00:15:04.991 --> 00:15:06.948
Speechy time! Yeah.

243
00:15:06.949 --> 00:15:08.341
Let's get this over with.

244
00:15:08.342 --> 00:15:10.561
Darrel. cut the creepy
tiddle-tunes.

245
00:15:10.562 --> 00:15:12.476
- Come on.
- Yes. sir.

