You know. the first thing
they try and take away from you

748
00:35:27.561 --> 00:35:29.952
is hope.
but I never let go of mine.

749
00:35:29.953 --> 00:35:32.956
And look what happened.
Basho's free. baby.

750
00:35:32.957 --> 00:35:35.567
Ha-ha! About time. too.

751
00:35:35.568 --> 00:35:38.484
Got a lot of people.
a lot of people countin' on me.

752
00:35:38.485 --> 00:35:41.639
I am with the resistance.

753
00:35:41.640 --> 00:35:44.793
Yeah. Ha-ha!
See. they try

754
00:35:44.794 --> 00:35:47.927
to use The Culling.
The Culling.

755
00:35:47.928 --> 00:35:50.495
to scare people from
joining our cause. but no.

756
00:35:50.496 --> 00:35:53.063
It's all lies and illusions
and everyone knows it.

757
00:35:53.064 --> 00:35:56.066
We're still strong...
still strong.

758
00:35:56.067 --> 00:35:57.502
[continues muttering]

759
00:35:57.503 --> 00:36:00.636
[unsettling music playing]

760
00:36:06.338 --> 00:36:08.948
Yes. yes. yes. yes. yes.

761
00:36:08.949 --> 00:36:11.190
Come. Come. Come.
Ha-ha-ha. Right.

762
00:36:11.191 --> 00:36:13.432
If we're going to
take down Hilda.

763
00:36:13.433 --> 00:36:15.129
we're going to need an army.

764
00:36:16.217 --> 00:36:19.394
Here we go.
That's where my people come in.

765
00:36:20.221 --> 00:36:22.658
Welcome to...

766
00:36:24.225 --> 00:36:26.161
the resistance.

767
00:36:26.162 --> 00:36:28.098
[door hinges creak]

768
00:36:29.143 --> 00:36:30.187
Hold on.

769
00:36:30.188 --> 00:36:31.666
[insects chirping]

770
00:36:31.667 --> 00:36:32.581
Okay. wait. Just hold...

771
00:36:32.582 --> 00:36:34.148
hold on. will you?

772
00:36:34.149 --> 00:36:36.498
What's going on? Fuck.

773
00:36:36.499 --> 00:36:38.848
[unsettling music playing]

774
00:36:43.636 --> 00:36:44.592
[Benny strains]

775
00:36:44.593 --> 00:36:45.550
[body thuds]

776
00:36:46.900 --> 00:36:48.510
[Basho] Whoa. whoa. whoa!
Benny. Benny!

777
00:36:48.511 --> 00:36:49.598
No. no. no.
He's with me.

778
00:36:49.599 --> 00:36:50.947
He helped me escape.

779
00:36:50.948 --> 00:36:52.297
Hey. hey. It's me.

780
00:36:53.298 --> 00:36:55.081
Hey. hey.

781
00:36:55.082 --> 00:36:56.822
Put that down.

782
00:36:56.823 --> 00:36:58.563
Huh? It's me.

783
00:36:58.564 --> 00:37:00.653
- [both laugh]
- [Basho] It's me.

784
00:37:00.654 --> 00:37:02.829
Oh. how are you. mate?

785
00:37:04.918 --> 00:37:07.442
Where is everyone?
Where's the rest of the team?

786
00:37:12.969 --> 00:37:14.709
Mapple apple camels.

787
00:37:14.710 --> 00:37:18.236
[Boy] <i>[VO] Mapple apple what?
That... that can't be right.</i>

788
00:37:19.324 --> 00:37:23.284
All of them? Ey?

789
00:37:23.285 --> 00:37:24.720
How?

790
00:37:27.157 --> 00:37:28.680
Dodo buns for long lamps.

791
00:37:28.681 --> 00:37:30.464
[Boy] <i>[VO] Uh-oh.
Can't read his lips.</i>

792
00:37:30.465 --> 00:37:33.207
<i>Is he mumbling?
In a different language?</i>

793
00:37:34.730 --> 00:37:35.904
Wait. wait. wait. Hold on.

794
00:37:35.905 --> 00:37:38.038
What about Yanmai?
Where is she?

795
00:37:38.039 --> 00:37:39.299
Yanmai.

796
00:37:39.300 --> 00:37:40.692
Momo parking lot.

797
00:37:40.693 --> 00:37:41.824
[Boy] <i>[VO] Probably
not saying that.</i>

798
00:37:41.825 --> 00:37:42.956
<i>Maybe if I concentrate.
I can...</i>

799
00:37:42.957 --> 00:37:44.261
Pick Pod Briefcase.

800
00:37:44.262 --> 00:37:45.567
[Boy] <i>[VO] Uh.
something about pickles.</i>

801
00:37:45.568 --> 00:37:46.915
Schnoogleboob Droptop.

802
00:37:46.916 --> 00:37:47.961
[Boy] <i>[VO] Are these words?
I don't...</i>

803
00:37:47.962 --> 00:37:49.222
Dodo buns for turtle bird.

804
00:37:49.223 --> 00:37:52.444
[Boy] <i>[VO] Dodo buns sound fun.
Oh-oh.</i>

805
00:37:52.445 --> 00:37:53.879
[cries]

806
00:37:53.880 --> 00:37:57.144
[Boy] <i>[VO] Oh. wait.
Dodo buns are not fun.</i>

807
00:37:57.145 --> 00:37:59.146
[sobs]

808
00:38:00.974 --> 00:38:03.542
[Boy] <i>[VO] I've never heard
a grown man cry.</i>

809
00:38:03.543 --> 00:38:06.131
<i>Not sure what it sounds like.</i>

810
00:38:06.132 --> 00:38:08.720
[screeching like a monkey]

811
00:38:08.721 --> 00:38:10.331
[Boy] <i>[VO] No.
that can't be it.</i>

812
00:38:10.332 --> 00:38:13.028
[cries]

813
00:38:13.029 --> 00:38:17.643
[Boy] <i>[VO] I'm sorry
about the... dodo buns.</i>

814
00:38:19.906 --> 00:38:20.994
Ey.

815
00:38:23.692 --> 00:38:26.304
Ah! That bitch
will pay for this!

816
00:38:26.305 --> 00:38:27.392
[chair clattering]

817
00:38:27.393 --> 00:38:30.090
[groans]

818
00:38:30.091 --> 00:38:32.788
[panting]

819
00:38:36.096 --> 00:38:38.227
You know what. Benny?

820
00:38:38.228 --> 00:38:40.666
We'll do it ourselves.
We have a secret weapon.

821
00:38:41.406 --> 00:38:42.580
[Boy] <i>[VO] He's talking
about me.</i>

822
00:38:42.581 --> 00:38:46.498
I saw this man
take down an entire squad

823
00:38:46.499 --> 00:38:47.976
of Van Der Koy soldiers.

824
00:38:47.977 --> 00:38:49.456
[Boy] <i>[VO] I did do that.</i>

825
00:38:49.457 --> 00:38:50.936
He killed over a hundred men.

826
00:38:50.937 --> 00:38:52.286
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Slight exaggeration.</i>

827
00:38:52.287 --> 00:38:53.504
With his bare hands.

828
00:38:53.505 --> 00:38:54.593
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Definitely not true.</i>

829
00:38:54.594 --> 00:38:56.855
No bullshit.

830
00:38:56.856 --> 00:38:59.380
Yeah. this...
This is our shot.

831
00:38:59.381 --> 00:39:01.860
[laughs] Yeah.

832
00:39:01.861 --> 00:39:05.517
You know. for the first time
in years as well.

833
00:39:05.518 --> 00:39:07.953
You know what I know?

834
00:39:07.954 --> 00:39:09.782
I know where Hilda is gonna be.

835
00:39:09.783 --> 00:39:11.087
- [Benny] Hm.
- Yes.

836
00:39:11.088 --> 00:39:12.218
[laughs]

837
00:39:12.219 --> 00:39:14.743
Yeah. all we need
is a way in.

838
00:39:15.396 --> 00:39:16.441
You know what time it is?

839
00:39:16.442 --> 00:39:17.528
Mm-hm.

840
00:39:17.529 --> 00:39:20.400
Plan time. [laughs]

841
00:39:20.401 --> 00:39:21.902
He punched the Tammy Tam.

842
00:39:21.903 --> 00:39:23.403
Devil pay the Tammy Tam.

843
00:39:23.404 --> 00:39:25.798
[Boy] <i>[VO] [confused]
Yeah. Go... go team.</i>

844
00:39:25.799 --> 00:39:27.451
[Benny] Okay.

845
00:39:27.452 --> 00:39:29.104
[papers rustle]

846
00:39:29.105 --> 00:39:31.368
[Basho] Here we go...

847
00:39:31.369 --> 00:39:33.632
[indistinct chatter]

848
00:39:39.464 --> 00:39:41.116
[electricity crackles]

849
00:39:41.117 --> 00:39:42.684
[voice over speaker] <i>Any
individual violating orders...</i>

850
00:39:42.685 --> 00:39:45.121
[distant siren wailing]

851
00:39:45.122 --> 00:39:47.254
[wings flapping]

852
00:39:52.128 --> 00:39:55.349
[emotional music playing]

853
00:40:08.275 --> 00:40:10.103
[Mina] <i>[VO] We're gonna find
our magical perfect place</i>

854
00:40:10.104 --> 00:40:11.887
<i>and stay there forever.</i>

855
00:40:13.585 --> 00:40:15.282
<i>You with me?</i>

856
00:40:16.762 --> 00:40:19.808
[indistinct voice over speaker]

857
00:40:21.593 --> 00:40:23.812
[wings flapping]

858
00:40:25.423 --> 00:40:26.814
We have reason to believe

859
00:40:26.815 --> 00:40:29.295
the entire Van Der Koy family
are in the mansion.

860
00:40:29.296 --> 00:40:31.777
The Van Der Koys are made up
of three siblings.

861
00:40:31.778 --> 00:40:34.214
Now Gideon.
he runs the streets.

862
00:40:34.215 --> 00:40:36.912
Melanie runs business and PR.

863
00:40:36.913 --> 00:40:40.698
June27.
she is head of security.

864
00:40:40.699 --> 00:40:43.266
And Glen.
he no longer has a head.

865
00:40:43.267 --> 00:40:45.833
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Mm-hm. sweaty palms.</i>

866
00:40:45.834 --> 00:40:50.142
Now. they all take orders
from Hilda.

867
00:40:50.143 --> 00:40:51.839
<i>[VO] Now. The Culling ceremony
starts at 10:00.</i>

868
00:40:51.840 --> 00:40:55.038
which means they're leaving
the house by 8:00. Yeah.

869
00:40:55.039 --> 00:40:58.238
That gives us a two-hour window
to get you in...

870
00:40:58.239 --> 00:40:59.804
[Boy] <i>[VO] Ah!</i>

871
00:40:59.805 --> 00:41:01.763
[Basho] <i>[VO] But you cannot
go in guns a-blazing.</i>

872
00:41:01.764 --> 00:41:03.330
<i>Security's going
to be airtight.</i>

873
00:41:05.288 --> 00:41:06.898
<i>Dining room!</i>

874
00:41:06.899 --> 00:41:08.117
That's where
Benny's plan comes in.

875
00:41:08.118 --> 00:41:09.422
Take it away. Benny boy.

876
00:41:09.423 --> 00:41:11.512
Go-go robot guitar the biscuit.

877
00:41:11.513 --> 00:41:12.818
[Boy] <i>[VO] Hold on.</i>

878
00:41:13.949 --> 00:41:15.560
[Benny] <i>[VO]
Sea diver ham man</i>

879
00:41:15.561 --> 00:41:17.039
<i>platter dance.</i>

880
00:41:17.040 --> 00:41:18.780
What the fuck?

881
00:41:18.781 --> 00:41:20.521
Hm. [laughs]

882
00:41:20.522 --> 00:41:22.480
Yeah.

883
00:41:23.785 --> 00:41:25.047
[Boy] <i>[VO] Do I need to
understand this?</i>

884
00:41:25.048 --> 00:41:26.221
We'll repeat the plan.

885
00:41:26.222 --> 00:41:27.571
[Boy] <i>[VO]
This feels important.</i>

886
00:41:27.572 --> 00:41:28.920
<i>This is the whole plan.</i>

887
00:41:28.921 --> 00:41:31.532
[Mina] Maybe just pretend
you understand.

888
00:41:31.533 --> 00:41:34.274
Keep nodding.
Look impressed.

889
00:41:35.275 --> 00:41:37.319
[Benny laughs]

890
00:41:37.320 --> 00:41:40.062
...bumper stump mop mop.
[laughs]

891
00:41:40.063 --> 00:41:41.280
Caplinky?

892
00:41:41.281 --> 00:41:43.152
[Boy] <i>[VO] Sure. Caplinky.</i>

893
00:41:44.110 --> 00:41:47.156
<i>Basho seems happy.
It must be a good plan.</i>

894
00:41:47.157 --> 00:41:48.506
I don't like this plan.

895
00:41:51.770 --> 00:41:53.293
[guns cocking]

896
00:41:54.294 --> 00:41:56.470
[Boy] <i>[VO] I bet the plan will
make sense when it happens.</i>

897
00:41:56.471 --> 00:41:57.905
<i>Like a magic trick.</i>

898
00:41:57.906 --> 00:41:59.559
<i>Lots of weird props.</i>

899
00:41:59.560 --> 00:42:02.040
<i>But then
something amazing happens.</i>

900
00:42:02.041 --> 00:42:05.544
<i>Except I'm the magician.
And I don't know magic.</i>

901
00:42:05.545 --> 00:42:08.971
Nobody knows magic.
That's why it's magical.

902
00:42:08.972 --> 00:42:12.399
[Boy] <i>[VO] Right.
So. this is fine.</i>

903
00:42:12.400 --> 00:42:14.053
This is fine.

904
00:42:17.143 --> 00:42:19.928
[laughing]

905
00:42:21.495 --> 00:42:24.542
[uplifting music playing]

906
00:42:32.724 --> 00:42:35.334
[VDK soldier grunts]

907
00:42:35.335 --> 00:42:37.859
[Boy] <i>[VO] Okay.
It's that kind of plan.</i>

908
00:42:39.208 --> 00:42:42.429
<i>Weapons. Danger.
We're going to war.</i>

909
00:42:42.430 --> 00:42:43.560
<i>It's wartime.</i>

910
00:42:43.561 --> 00:42:45.084
<i>Just give me a weapon and...</i>

911
00:42:45.998 --> 00:42:47.434
Now comes the hard part.

912
00:42:49.001 --> 00:42:51.045
Tramp stamp skidmark.

913
00:42:51.046 --> 00:42:54.484
[Boy] <i>[VO] Befuddled.
To be deeply confused.</i>

914
00:42:54.485 --> 00:42:56.965
<i>Deeply. deeply confused.</i>

915
00:42:56.966 --> 00:42:59.446
[party music nearby]

916
00:42:59.447 --> 00:43:01.579
[bird calling]

917
00:43:03.058 --> 00:43:05.931
[soothing music playing]

918
00:43:08.586 --> 00:43:09.630
[Mina] Finally!

919
00:43:09.631 --> 00:43:10.804
Disguises!

920
00:43:10.805 --> 00:43:12.372
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Right. I'm a chef.</i>

921
00:43:12.373 --> 00:43:13.981
<i>Why am I a chef?</i>

922
00:43:13.982 --> 00:43:16.681
[Kramer] The dinner scene
will commence very soon.

923
00:43:16.682 --> 00:43:19.118
Start plating the crème brûlée.

924
00:43:19.901 --> 00:43:21.467
[Boy] <i>[VO] I don't know
what that means.</i>

925
00:43:21.468 --> 00:43:23.992
<i>How do I plate a crème?
Why am I crème plating?!</i>

926
00:43:23.993 --> 00:43:25.603
[Mina] Don't blow your cover.

927
00:43:25.604 --> 00:43:27.561
Just act chef-y.

928
00:43:32.044 --> 00:43:35.134
[man singing
in foreign language]

929
00:43:39.791 --> 00:43:41.357
Oh. macarons!

930
00:43:44.534 --> 00:43:45.709
Try one.

931
00:43:45.710 --> 00:43:47.885
Chefs eat things.

932
00:43:47.886 --> 00:43:50.671
[Boy] <i>[VO] Fine. One macaron.</i>

933
00:43:51.237 --> 00:43:54.457
<i>but then I need to find...
What was that?</i>

934
00:43:54.458 --> 00:43:55.936
Macaron.

935
00:43:55.937 --> 00:43:57.873
[Boy] <i>[VO] That's delicious.</i>

936
00:43:57.874 --> 00:44:00.321
Eat more.
You're a chef.

937
00:44:00.322 --> 00:44:02.770
[man continues singing]

938
00:44:04.685 --> 00:44:05.730
[Boy's satisfied giggle]

939
00:44:05.731 --> 00:44:07.383
<i>Strawberry.</i>

940
00:44:07.384 --> 00:44:09.036
<i>Caramel.</i>

941
00:44:09.037 --> 00:44:10.821
<i>Vanilla.</i>

942
00:44:10.822 --> 00:44:13.389
<i>So soft and squishy.</i>

943
00:44:14.913 --> 00:44:15.956
[Mina] Oh.

944
00:44:15.957 --> 00:44:17.176
[Boy] <i>[VO] Uh-oh.</i>

945
00:44:18.481 --> 00:44:19.787
He's not happy.

946
00:44:21.049 --> 00:44:24.399
[muttered dialogue]

947
00:44:24.400 --> 00:44:26.750
[Kramer] Good evening.
Happy Culling.

948
00:44:26.751 --> 00:44:29.536
Gideon has prepared a most
delectable menu for you all.

949
00:44:40.199 --> 00:44:42.113
[Boy] <i>[VO] I am an instrument.</i>

950
00:44:42.114 --> 00:44:44.746
<i>Shaped for a single purpose.
To kill...</i>

951
00:44:44.747 --> 00:44:47.379
[Mina] You don't look
like an instrument.

952
00:44:47.380 --> 00:44:48.903
[Boy] <i>[VO] I'm gonna go
take care of something.</i>

953
00:44:48.904 --> 00:44:51.209
<i>Alone. You stay here</i>

954
00:44:51.210 --> 00:44:53.647
<i>and grab all the macarons
you can find.</i>

955
00:44:53.648 --> 00:44:55.082
<i>And when I'm done.</i>

956
00:44:55.083 --> 00:44:58.478
<i>we'll bring them to
our magical perfect place.</i>

957
00:44:58.479 --> 00:44:59.826
<i>Sound good?</i>

958
00:44:59.827 --> 00:45:02.046
Mission accepted.

959
00:45:02.047 --> 00:45:03.657
But what are you going to do?

960
00:45:04.832 --> 00:45:06.072
[Boy] <i>[VO]
I'm gonna act chef-y.</i>

961
00:45:07.705 --> 00:45:09.445
[suspenseful music playing]

962
00:45:13.145 --> 00:45:14.233
[door bangs open]

963
00:45:15.364 --> 00:45:16.496
[grater thuds]

964
00:45:22.067 --> 00:45:23.851
Still waiting on the crème...

965
00:45:23.852 --> 00:45:25.330
[clanging]

966
00:45:25.331 --> 00:45:27.267
[knives clanking]

967
00:45:27.268 --> 00:45:29.204
[frying pan thuds]

968
00:45:32.381 --> 00:45:33.991
[clanking]

969
00:45:33.992 --> 00:45:35.297
[female chef grunts]

970
00:45:37.038 --> 00:45:40.389
- Aahh!
- [blood splatters]

971
00:45:40.390 --> 00:45:42.261
Aahh!

972
00:45:43.392 --> 00:45:46.068
[grunting]

973
00:45:46.069 --> 00:45:47.929
[clanking]

974
00:45:47.930 --> 00:45:49.789
[grates skin]

975
00:45:49.790 --> 00:45:50.922
[slices with knife]

976
00:45:50.923 --> 00:45:52.184
[grates face]

977
00:45:53.925 --> 00:45:55.317
[grater thuds]

978
00:45:56.841 --> 00:45:57.885
[knife clanks]

979
00:46:05.240 --> 00:46:06.285
[slits throat]

980
00:46:09.114 --> 00:46:10.201
[head chopped]

981
00:46:10.202 --> 00:46:13.726
[blood splattering]

982
00:46:13.727 --> 00:46:15.728
[Boy] <i>[VO] I did it! Yes!</i>

983
00:46:15.729 --> 00:46:17.731
<i>Player One wins!</i>

984
00:46:17.732 --> 00:46:18.731
[screaming]

985
00:46:18.732 --> 00:46:20.125
[Boy] <i>[VO] Uh. wait.</i>

986
00:46:21.648 --> 00:46:22.953
<i>They look different.</i>

987
00:46:22.954 --> 00:46:24.563
<i>Why do they look so different?</i>

988
00:46:24.564 --> 00:46:26.500
He just chopped
a fucking head off.

989
00:46:26.501 --> 00:46:28.437
[Boy] <i>[VO] Something's off.</i>

990
00:46:31.397 --> 00:46:34.007
- [woman screams]
- [head thuds]

991
00:46:34.008 --> 00:46:36.619
[Boy] <i>[VO] Did I kill
the wrong Hilda?</i>

992
00:46:36.620 --> 00:46:37.576
Gotcha.

993
00:46:37.577 --> 00:46:38.926
Oh. oh. oh. oh.

994
