01:13:00.332 --> 01:13:03.466
Remember the first thing
they try and take from you?

1494
01:13:03.467 --> 01:13:04.945
[Boy] <i>[VO] Hope.</i>

1495
01:13:08.166 --> 01:13:09.385
Don't you ever lose it.

1496
01:13:12.344 --> 01:13:13.823
Come on.

1497
01:13:13.824 --> 01:13:16.000
See you soon. Benny.

1498
01:13:16.001 --> 01:13:18.394
[groans]

1499
01:13:20.439 --> 01:13:21.700
You know. I just...

1500
01:13:21.701 --> 01:13:24.008
I just realized
you don't talk much. do you?

1501
01:13:25.183 --> 01:13:26.184
I like it.

1502
01:13:29.535 --> 01:13:30.797
Go!

1503
01:13:33.452 --> 01:13:34.714
[blood splatters]

1504
01:13:36.194 --> 01:13:37.413
[rapid gunfire]

1505
01:13:41.678 --> 01:13:42.809
[blood splatters]

1506
01:13:44.158 --> 01:13:45.158
[knife clanks]

1507
01:13:46.160 --> 01:13:47.770
Don't look back.

1508
01:13:47.771 --> 01:13:49.381
Give 'em hell. Go!

1509
01:13:49.382 --> 01:13:52.340
[panting]

1510
01:13:55.996 --> 01:13:57.693
[Boy] <i>[VO] Extirpate.</i>

1511
01:13:57.694 --> 01:14:01.045
<i>To destroy every motherfucker
that gets in my way.</i>

1512
01:14:01.046 --> 01:14:02.219
Ahh!

1513
01:14:02.220 --> 01:14:03.220
Give 'em hell.

1514
01:14:04.048 --> 01:14:07.138
[straining]

1515
01:14:17.104 --> 01:14:18.192
[gun fired]

1516
01:14:26.026 --> 01:14:28.551
[Mina] <i>[VO] Imagine
our magical perfect place.</i>

1517
01:14:35.993 --> 01:14:37.559
- [blood splatters]
- [screaming]

1518
01:14:37.560 --> 01:14:39.126
[Mina] <i>[VO] Can you see it?</i>

1519
01:14:39.127 --> 01:14:42.129
[panting]

1520
01:15:07.851 --> 01:15:10.179
[Gideon groaning]

1521
01:15:10.180 --> 01:15:12.508
[flask clanking]

1522
01:15:16.424 --> 01:15:17.774
Hmm.

1523
01:15:19.210 --> 01:15:20.907
[exhales]

1524
01:15:24.258 --> 01:15:28.306
Probably was expecting
a showdown. huh?

1525
01:15:29.220 --> 01:15:31.483
Classic boss fight.

1526
01:15:33.746 --> 01:15:35.007
Sorry to disappoint.

1527
01:15:35.008 --> 01:15:37.924
Bitch sister Melanie
shot me in the back.

1528
01:15:40.623 --> 01:15:42.233
And she's the nice one.

1529
01:15:49.501 --> 01:15:51.285
You'll need this.

1530
01:15:52.504 --> 01:15:53.897
They evacuated.

1531
01:15:55.072 --> 01:15:57.204
They're in the bunker.
That's where you'll find her.

1532
01:16:06.779 --> 01:16:08.019
[katana clanks]

1533
01:16:08.020 --> 01:16:09.260
Yeah. well.

1534
01:16:10.566 --> 01:16:12.089
Do what you got to do.

1535
01:16:20.706 --> 01:16:22.315
He helped us.

1536
01:16:22.316 --> 01:16:24.491
[Boy] <i>[VO] No more
distractions.</i>

1537
01:16:24.492 --> 01:16:27.191
You can't just keep
killing everybody.

1538
01:16:27.887 --> 01:16:29.585
[Boy] <i>[VO] You're not real.</i>

1539
01:16:30.194 --> 01:16:32.369
Listen to me.
I'm your sister...

1540
01:16:32.370 --> 01:16:34.546
[Boy] <i>[VO]
My sister is dead.</i>

1541
01:16:41.684 --> 01:16:43.555
<i>I don't need you anymore.</i>

1542
01:16:55.045 --> 01:16:56.350
Huh.

1543
01:16:59.658 --> 01:17:01.486
[katana clanks]

1544
01:17:10.147 --> 01:17:11.888
[elevator door closes]

1545
01:17:18.677 --> 01:17:20.244
[elevator rumbles]

1546
01:17:28.905 --> 01:17:30.406
[screen screeches]

1547
01:17:30.407 --> 01:17:31.907
<i>Ding dong.</i>

1548
01:17:31.908 --> 01:17:34.300
<i>You have reached
your final destination.</i>

1549
01:17:34.301 --> 01:17:36.739
<i>In a few moment.
our lovely ground crew</i>

1550
01:17:36.740 --> 01:17:38.043
<i>will open the doors.</i>

1551
01:17:38.044 --> 01:17:40.394
<i>unload a flurry
of armor-piercing bullets</i>

1552
01:17:40.395 --> 01:17:42.353
<i>and shred you to pieces.</i>

1553
01:17:43.136 --> 01:17:46.662
<i>You will die alone
and forgotten.</i>

1554
01:17:47.532 --> 01:17:48.968
<i>All for nothing.</i>

1555
01:17:49.839 --> 01:17:52.450
[Boy] <i>[VO]
No. Not for nothing.</i>

1556
01:17:54.931 --> 01:17:56.541
<i>This is for her.</i>

1557
01:17:57.716 --> 01:18:00.632
[emotional music playing]

1558
01:18:05.593 --> 01:18:07.552
[elevator beeps]

1559
01:18:12.470 --> 01:18:13.731
[katana clanks]

1560
01:18:13.732 --> 01:18:16.648
[tense. suspenseful music
playing]

1561
01:18:20.043 --> 01:18:21.697
[elevator door opens]

1562
01:18:34.187 --> 01:18:35.275
[helmet beeps]

1563
01:18:37.800 --> 01:18:39.844
[katana clanks]

1564
01:18:39.845 --> 01:18:42.979
[tense music playing]

1565
01:19:02.259 --> 01:19:03.695
[whispering]

1566
01:19:04.609 --> 01:19:07.699
[dramatic music]

1567
01:19:16.012 --> 01:19:17.665
[Boy] <i>[VO] One purpose...</i>

1568
01:19:17.666 --> 01:19:20.538
[echoing whispers]

1569
01:19:23.019 --> 01:19:25.499
[Boy] <i>[VO]
One purpose only.</i>

1570
01:19:25.500 --> 01:19:26.805
<i>Kill them all...</i>

1571
01:19:26.806 --> 01:19:28.110
[echoing whispers]

1572
01:19:28.111 --> 01:19:29.394
[Boy] <i>[VO] To kill her.</i>

1573
01:19:29.395 --> 01:19:31.124
<i>...instrument...</i>

1574
01:19:31.125 --> 01:19:32.854
[echoing whispers]

1575
01:19:32.855 --> 01:19:35.118
[Boy] <i>[VO]
Kill Hilda Van Der Koy.</i>

1576
01:19:35.119 --> 01:19:38.295
[emotional music playing]

1577
01:20:01.274 --> 01:20:03.320
[Hilda] It really is you.
isn't it?

1578
01:20:06.540 --> 01:20:10.762
I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry
I didn't recognize you.

1579
01:20:13.243 --> 01:20:15.158
He convinced us you were dead.

1580
01:20:17.116 --> 01:20:19.640
Oh. but here you are.

1581
01:20:22.992 --> 01:20:24.732
You remember me. don't you?

1582
01:20:27.605 --> 01:20:28.649
It's me.

1583
01:20:29.912 --> 01:20:31.565
Your mother.

1584
01:20:35.308 --> 01:20:37.396
He did this to you.

1585
01:20:37.397 --> 01:20:39.443
He made you forget
what you are.

1586
01:20:45.362 --> 01:20:47.364
The things he must have
done to you.

1587
01:20:49.409 --> 01:20:51.063
I can only imagine.

1588
01:21:01.900 --> 01:21:03.815
[coughs]

1589
01:21:05.208 --> 01:21:06.862
[Shaman] <i>[VO]
Is this your mother?</i>

1590
01:21:08.515 --> 01:21:10.387
[slap thrown]

1591
01:21:12.650 --> 01:21:14.565
<i>Your mother is dead. boy.</i>

1592
01:21:18.264 --> 01:21:19.700
[slap thrown]

1593
01:21:22.007 --> 01:21:23.574
<i>This is your mother.</i>

1594
01:21:27.665 --> 01:21:30.189
<i>Your mother is dead.</i>

1595
01:21:34.019 --> 01:21:35.978
<i>Hilda did this to you.</i>

1596
01:21:35.979 --> 01:21:37.196
[groans]

1597
01:21:38.067 --> 01:21:39.938
[screams in pain]

1598
01:21:41.157 --> 01:21:42.636
[blood splatters]

1599
01:21:42.637 --> 01:21:43.985
[screams]

1600
01:21:43.986 --> 01:21:46.553
[Shaman] <i>[VO]
Hilda killed your family.</i>

1601
01:21:47.598 --> 01:21:49.861
<i>I saved you.</i>

1602
01:21:50.906 --> 01:21:52.864
[laughing evilly]

1603
01:21:58.000 --> 01:22:00.284
[screaming angrily]

1604
01:22:00.285 --> 01:22:02.569
[laughing evilly]

1605
01:22:04.484 --> 01:22:05.921
[Hilda] <i>[VO] It's me.</i>

1606
01:22:08.662 --> 01:22:09.925
<i>Your mother...</i>

1607
01:22:17.062 --> 01:22:18.542
Yes.

1608
01:22:31.947 --> 01:22:34.862
[crowd applauding]

1609
01:22:36.299 --> 01:22:38.083
[Mina] <i>[VO] Can you see it?</i>

1610
01:22:41.521 --> 01:22:43.175
<i>I can see it too.</i>

1611
01:22:49.921 --> 01:22:51.967
[Hilda] Look at him.

1612
01:22:52.445 --> 01:22:54.751
This man killed your father.

1613
01:22:54.752 --> 01:22:57.233
Trained soldiers
to destroy our family.

1614
01:22:58.321 --> 01:23:00.670
He thought we were weak.

1615
01:23:00.671 --> 01:23:03.021
We're not weak. are we?

1616
01:23:03.022 --> 01:23:04.196
Are we?!

1617
01:23:07.199 --> 01:23:08.874
Yes. just like that.

1618
01:23:08.875 --> 01:23:10.550
Just like we practiced.

1619
01:23:12.335 --> 01:23:14.946
[Shaman] Please.
Spare the children.

1620
01:23:14.947 --> 01:23:16.861
Please.

1621
01:23:16.862 --> 01:23:18.384
Please!

1622
01:23:18.385 --> 01:23:19.906
No!

1623
01:23:19.907 --> 01:23:21.474
[rapid gunfire]

1624
01:23:24.695 --> 01:23:26.392
[crying]

1625
01:23:26.393 --> 01:23:28.090
[shaking]

1626
01:23:31.093 --> 01:23:33.529
Aahhh!

1627
01:23:33.530 --> 01:23:35.662
[Hilda] <i>[VO]
Make your family proud.</i>

1628
01:23:35.663 --> 01:23:36.881
End this.

1629
01:23:45.063 --> 01:23:46.760
[rapid gunfire]

1630
01:23:46.761 --> 01:23:47.891
Ah!

1631
01:23:47.892 --> 01:23:49.415
Kill him! Go!

1632
01:23:53.115 --> 01:23:56.205
[Hilda]
It's okay. It's okay.

1633
01:23:59.643 --> 01:24:01.036
[panting]

1634
01:24:03.690 --> 01:24:06.693
[crying]

1635
01:24:15.746 --> 01:24:19.054
[choking]

1636
01:24:20.968 --> 01:24:22.405
[Shaman straining]

1637
01:24:26.061 --> 01:24:28.063
[breathing heavily]

1638
01:24:39.596 --> 01:24:42.185
[Hilda] He used you
to orchestrate his revenge.

1639
01:24:42.186 --> 01:24:44.775
Turned you against me.
Against your family.

1640
01:24:50.563 --> 01:24:52.608
Against your own sister.

1641
01:24:52.609 --> 01:24:54.654
[June27 panting softly]

1642
01:24:54.655 --> 01:24:55.699
[thud]

1643
01:24:59.355 --> 01:25:00.617
[Boy] <i>[VO] Mina.</i>

1644
01:25:09.843 --> 01:25:11.410
[Hilda] I did it for us.

1645
01:25:13.151 --> 01:25:14.761
For you.

1646
01:25:16.067 --> 01:25:18.504
Because I love you.
And he took you from me.

1647
01:25:23.901 --> 01:25:25.946
I spent years
hunting for him.

1648
01:25:28.166 --> 01:25:30.516
I see him everywhere I go.

1649
01:25:30.517 --> 01:25:32.039
He is poison. like...

1650
01:25:32.649 --> 01:25:35.826
like sharp embers.
scraping behind my eyes.

1651
01:25:38.481 --> 01:25:41.157
But tonight.
tonight was different.

1652
01:25:41.158 --> 01:25:43.834
He was there.
In that audience.

1653
01:25:43.835 --> 01:25:45.530
Watching.

1654
01:25:45.531 --> 01:25:48.665
[suspenseful music playing]

1655
01:25:52.103 --> 01:25:53.800
Tell me. [slaps hard]

1656
01:25:57.413 --> 01:25:58.935
I'm so sorry.

1657
01:25:58.936 --> 01:26:01.808
I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.
It's not your fault.

1658
01:26:01.809 --> 01:26:03.832
No. no. no.
He put you under his spell.

1659
01:26:03.833 --> 01:26:05.855
A spell that won't end
until he's dead.

1660
01:26:05.856 --> 01:26:09.207
Just. please. Please show me
you're still in there.

1661
01:26:09.208 --> 01:26:10.861
my sweet. sweet boy.

1662
01:26:10.862 --> 01:26:12.515
Come back to me. Please.

1663
01:26:14.299 --> 01:26:15.605
Please.

1664
01:26:31.577 --> 01:26:33.275
This isn't your brother.

1665
01:26:35.755 --> 01:26:38.062
Everything he once was
has been stripped away.

1666
01:26:39.933 --> 01:26:41.544
He's lost to us.

1667
01:26:51.162 --> 01:26:53.382
The Shaman wants us dead.

1668
01:26:53.383 --> 01:26:55.644
This is his weapon.

1669
01:26:55.645 --> 01:26:57.864
Deal with him accordingly.

1670
01:26:59.301 --> 01:27:02.956
[tense music playing]

1671
01:27:15.230 --> 01:27:16.709
[smashes tomahawk]

1672
01:27:20.496 --> 01:27:21.627
[kick thrown]

1673
01:27:23.368 --> 01:27:24.804
[Boy grunts]

1674
01:27:27.198 --> 01:27:28.243
[tomahawk clanks]

1675
01:27:37.556 --> 01:27:40.777
[emotional music playing]

1676
01:27:53.180 --> 01:27:54.225
Finish it!

1677
01:27:56.358 --> 01:27:57.837
[stabs tomahawk]

1678
01:28:02.712 --> 01:28:04.061
[blood splatters]

1679
01:28:04.062 --> 01:28:05.149
[body thuds]

1680
01:28:09.893 --> 01:28:11.655
[cries]

1681
01:28:11.656 --> 01:28:13.418
Get them!

1682
01:28:14.637 --> 01:28:17.857
[rapid gunfire]

1683
01:28:22.122 --> 01:28:24.255
The only way out
is the way that we came in!

1684
01:28:24.256 --> 01:28:25.822
We've gotta make a run for it!

1685
01:28:27.737 --> 01:28:29.412
[Boy] <i>[VO] Okay.</i>

1686
01:28:29.413 --> 01:28:31.087
<i>Okay...</i>

1687
01:28:31.088 --> 01:28:32.088
[June27 panting]

1688
01:28:32.089 --> 01:28:33.090
<i>...let's do this.</i>

1689
01:28:34.874 --> 01:28:36.005
[grunts]

1690
01:28:36.006 --> 01:28:37.441
[rapid gunfire]

1691
01:28:37.442 --> 01:28:38.878
["I Get Mine" performed by
El Michels Affair playing]

1692
01:28:38.879 --> 01:28:40.314
<i>♪ What you want
Is what you get ♪</i>

1693
01:28:40.315 --> 01:28:41.532
<i>♪ All this time.
I didn't forget ♪</i>

1694
01:28:41.533 --> 01:28:43.274
<i>♪ I don't know
What I've been told ♪</i>

1695
01:28:43.275 --> 01:28:44.840
<i>♪ But I'll find my way</i>

1696
01:28:44.841 --> 01:28:46.364
<i>- ♪ And I'll crack the code ♪</i>
- [June27 strains]

1697
01:28:46.365 --> 01:28:48.323
- [rapid gunfire]
<i>- ♪ I get mine</i>

1698
01:28:48.324 --> 01:28:52.239
<i>♪ I get mine</i>

1699
01:28:52.240 --> 01:28:55.220
[rapid gunfire]

1700
01:28:55.221 --> 01:28:58.201
<i>♪ Mine</i>

1701
01:28:58.202 --> 01:29:02.032
<i>♪ I get mine</i>

1702
01:29:03.338 --> 01:29:05.556
[rapid gunfire]

1703
01:29:05.557 --> 01:29:07.711
[Boy] <i>[VO] Shit!</i>

1704
01:29:07.712 --> 01:29:09.866
[rapid gunfire]

1705
01:29:10.736 --> 01:29:12.977
[blood splatters]

1706
01:29:12.978 --> 01:29:15.219
[rapid gunfire]

1707
01:29:24.924 --> 01:29:28.623
<i>♪ I get mine</i>

1708
01:29:28.624 --> 01:29:32.323
[rapid gunfire]

1709
01:29:40.287 --> 01:29:43.420
[grunting]

1710
01:29:43.421 --> 01:29:45.815
[rapid gunfire]

1711
01:29:47.904 --> 01:29:49.993
[shield clanking]

1712
01:29:55.477 --> 01:29:56.781
Ahhhh!

1713
01:29:56.782 --> 01:29:59.045
[rapid gunfire]

1714
01:30:27.552 --> 01:30:30.773
- [rapid gunfire]
- [VDK soldier grunting]

1715
01:30:32.165 --> 01:30:33.950
[panting]

1716
01:30:35.517 --> 01:30:36.952
[indistinct chatter]

1717
01:30:36.953 --> 01:30:39.237
[June27] Come on!

1718
01:30:39.238 --> 01:30:41.523
[rapid gunfire]

1719
01:30:44.351 --> 01:30:46.571
[banging elevator door]

1720
01:30:46.572 --> 01:30:49.008
[elevator beeps]

1721
01:30:49.009 --> 01:30:51.446
[both panting]

1722
01:31:01.456 --> 01:31:03.458
I never stopped
looking for you.

1723
01:31:05.982 --> 01:31:07.505
They told me the Shaman
had killed you.

1724
01:31:07.506 --> 01:31:09.072
but I never stopped.

1725
01:31:11.161 --> 01:31:13.816
If I had my chance. none of this
would have ever happened.

1726
01:31:18.821 --> 01:31:24.914
[Boy] <i>[VO] Liminal.
To exist between two states.</i>

1727
01:31:25.958 --> 01:31:28.570
I hated them
for taking you away from me.

1728
01:31:29.571 --> 01:31:31.050
All of them.

1729
01:31:33.792 --> 01:31:35.881
I wanted them to suffer.

1730
01:31:38.449 --> 01:31:40.059
And they did.

1731
01:31:41.408 --> 01:31:43.193
Every last one of them.

1732
01:31:49.547 --> 01:31:51.114
[echoing] Hey.

1733
01:31:51.115 --> 01:31:52.507
Hey...

1734
01:31:54.465 --> 01:31:55.858
Are you okay?

1735
01:31:58.425 --> 01:32:02.299
[electricity crackles.
elevator beeps]

1736
01:32:16.008 --> 01:32:18.489
[elevator pings. opening]

1737
01:32:22.232 --> 01:32:25.191
[water trickling]

1738
01:32:39.641 --> 01:32:41.556
[in sign language]
You have done well.

1739
01:32:49.520 --> 01:32:51.391
You got what you wanted.

1740
01:32:52.001 --> 01:32:53.001
She's dead.

1741
01:32:54.003 --> 01:32:55.178
They're all dead.

1742
01:32:58.790 --> 01:33:00.575
Not all of them.

1743
01:33:18.549 --> 01:33:19.985
[coat thuds]

1744
01:33:22.553 --> 01:33:24.207
Hey. motherfucker.

1745
01:33:27.558 --> 01:33:29.168
This ends now.

1746
01:33:35.653 --> 01:33:37.263
- [kick thrown]
- [Shaman groans]

1747
01:33:38.874 --> 01:33:41.964
- [punches and kicks thrown]
- [both grunting]

1748
01:33:46.446 --> 01:33:48.100
- [punches and kicks thrown]
- [grunting continues]

1749
01:33:48.101 --> 01:33:50.014
[blood splatters]

1750
01:33:50.015 --> 01:33:52.627
- [punches and kicks thrown]
- [grunting continues]

1751
01:33:57.675 --> 01:33:59.416
